Package semkit.demos

Use these demos to see various applications of the semantic kit.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApiCallSample
    Sample Java API Caller for Wikimeta.
    BuildHtmlSample
    Build an HTML file using the Wikimeta API.
    LODRetrievalSample
    This is an example to demonstrate how to retrieve data from the Linked Open Data according to an existing entity.

    www.wikimeta.org www.wikimeta.com
    Update April 2012
    RedisNLGbAseSample
    This sample helps to use and understand the Redis Base and NLGbAse metadata access.

    Command line samples:

    - How to read a metadata for a given entity (entity using wikipedia key):

    java -cp semlinker.jar semkit.demos.RedisNLGbAseSample -TestEnt Canada

    - How to find available metadata for a given surface form:

    java -cp semlinker semkit.demos.RedisNLGbAseSample -TestKey challenger

    CAUTION: do not forget to have Redis Base and server active !!!
    SemanticExtractorSample
    This class is an example of a complete annotation and LOD extraction process.
